data.description: Welcome to this exquisite cul-de-sac lot home nestled in a charming community in close proximity to parks, lakes, and a variety of restaurants. Step inside to discover a thoughtfully designed interior with fresh paint. The main level boasts an inviting office space, ideal for remote work, and a formal dining area, perfect for gatherings. A cozy breakfast nook perfectly complements the spacious kitchen adorned with granite countertops and an abundance of cabinet space. The living room features built-in shelving and a fireplace that radiates warmth and charm. The primary bedroom is complete with an ensuite bath boasting dual vanities, a jetted tub, and not 1 but 2 closets! Upstairs, a generously sized game room offers boundless potential for entertainment while the balcony provides enchanting views of the fully fenced backyard with ample green space for outdoor activities. Easy access to I 45, Hardy Toll Road, & 99 Grand Pkwy. Don't miss the opportunity to make this stunning home yours!
